medpolish Ply df config

Source: R/tidyMS_aggregation.R
medpolishPlydf_config.Rd

medpolish Ply df config

medpolishPlydf_config(pdata, config, name = FALSE)

Arguments

pdata

data.frame
config

AnalysisConfiguration

See also

Other aggregation: INTERNAL_FUNCTIONS_BY_FAMILY, aggregateTopNIntensities(), aggregate_intensity(), intensity_summary_by_hkeys(), medpolishPlydf(), medpolishPly(), medpolish_protein_quants(), plot_aggregation(), plot_hierarchies_add_quantline(), plot_hierarchies_line_df(), plot_hierarchies_line(), summarizeRobust_config(), summarizeRobust()

Examples

library(tidyverse)
bb <- prolfqua::data_ionstar$filtered()
#> Column added : nr_peptide_Id_IN_protein_Id
stopifnot(nrow(bb$data) == 25780)
conf <- bb$config
data <- bb$data
conf$table$hierarchyDepth = 1
xnested <- data %>%
  group_by_at(conf$table$hkeysDepth()) %>% tidyr::nest()

feature <- setdiff(conf$table$hierarchyKeys(),  conf$table$hkeysDepth())
x <- xnested$data[[1]]
bb <- medpolishPlydf_config(x,conf)
prolfqua:::.reestablish_condition(x,bb, conf)
